Fred Walton (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fred_Walton_(actor) 0 Fred Walton (July 26, 1865 – December 28, 1936) was an English stage actor who immigrated to the United States in the early part of the 20th century and became a character actor in American silent and early sound films.
